{"title":"短歌四首","authors":["徐放"],"dates":[{"year":1992,"month":6,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"短歌四首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"徐放"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"徐放赠日本著名俳人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伊藤柏翠先生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天桥迎嘉宾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俳人歌手来东邻；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捧杯为洗尘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫道他乡无知己，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天下谁人不识翁！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有　赠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——迎“日本传统俳句协会友好访华团”，念及日本友人千叶宣一教授"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一别几岁星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不觉满头已改青；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎客倍思君。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"酬唱往事犹记否？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"襟上杭州旧酒痕！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寄佐藤和夫教授"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西湖结伴行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曲水流觞集兰亭；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风微雨又晴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别后思君常入梦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"至今魂绕越王城！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赠“日本传统俳句协会友好访华团”诸俳人歌手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燕都喜相逢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明晚即将唱渭城；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别也太倥偬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他年愿同姑苏去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"客船卧听夜半钟！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}